To prove the Tutte-Berge formula in Lean 4, we need to show that for any graph $G$ and subset $Y \subseteq V(G)$, the size of a maximum matching $\nu(G)$ satisfies:
$$ \nu(G) \leq \frac{1}{2}(|V(G)| + |Y| - \text{odd}(G - Y)) $$
