# Solving the Tutte-Berge Formula in Lean 4

We need to prove the Tutte-Berge formula for the size of a maximum matching in an arbitrary graph. The formula states that $\nu(G) = \min_{Z \subseteq V} \frac{1}{2}(|V| + |Z| - \text{odd}(G - Z))$, where $\nu(G)$ is the size of a maximum matching, $V$ is the vertex set, and $\text{odd}(G - Z)$ is the number of components of $G - Z$ with an odd number of vertices.

