3. **Combine**: Using the above, $\nu(G) = \nu(G - X) + |X| = \frac{1}{2}(|V(G - X)| - \text{odd}(G - X)) + |X| = \frac{1}{2}(|V| + |X| - \text{odd}(G - X))$.
